text: AIK Bandy is a bandy club in Solna in Sweden. Established in 1905, the club won the Swedish national men's bandy championship in the years of 1909, 1914 and 1931. ==References== ==Other websites== *AIK Bandy Category:1905 establishments in Europe Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden Category:1900s establishments in Sweden
